                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Est donc vieux malgré son jeune âge !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Jamais sourire plus narquois\nN'a ridé plus hideux visage.\nQue ce pâtre à jambe de bois\nEst donc vieux malgré son jeune âge !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Voici que ma chienne aux abois",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Flaire un calamiteux présage ;",
